analysis.reasoning: Version A surfaces a higher proportion of bicycles in the top slots (e‑bikes, fatbike, city bikes) which is more relevant for the broad query “Fietsen”. Top results in A include popular models and best‑seller badges and show a good mix of bike types, giving better immediate user value. Version B places several accessories (tire, lock, small electronic sensor) among the highest positions which reduces relevance for users primarily looking for bicycles.
